  "description": "PRYZM 2 — composition root (S73 / Phase A of PRYZM2-ENTERPRISE-WIREUP-PLAN-S72). Owns `composeRuntime()` — the one place where every L0–L7.5 piece is constructed and joined into a single typed `PryzmRuntime` handle. The handle is the contract between the white UI (`src/ui/`) and the engine; per the lint rule landed in Phase H, `src/ui/` may import only `@pryzm/runtime-composer/types`. This is not a bridge: it is a one-shot wire-up.",
